--- !u!114 &610017066
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 610017063}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9f26d31590dbf4fc395a38f09d5bcea9, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  characters:
  - characterName: Stone
    characterStory: "Stone is the eldest of the family members.  He is like a father
      to all.  He is conservative and always the philosopher.  The entire family
      looks up to Stone often coming to him for advice. He is laid back. Fair play
      is important to him!\n\nStone\u2019s lifestyle is like his sport \u2013 slow,
      direct and always patient.  He moves slowly and conservatively.  He is a plodder.
      \n\nStone\u2019s message \u2013 Never, Never give up.  Be patient \u2013 \u201Cslow
      and steady wins the race.\u201D \n\nStone\u2019s mark \u2013 a broom used as
      his sweeper."
    characterModel: {fileID: 2368810525428554514}
    price: 1500
    isUnlocked: 0
    selectedSkinIndex: 0
    skins:
    - skinName: 
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: a650533c61987468393d3095276645e2, type: 2}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99a05cea3fbcb442cb1b81e0bf8771af, type: 3}
      price: 0
      isUnlocked: 0
    - skinName: 
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: d4789fbbf15504be398b9f66e18804a9, type: 2}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f621e08cdf315405e98f714a5bf65107, type: 3}
      price: 0
      isUnlocked: 0
    - skinName: 
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: 6ce84c03e504a4375b2776d15d5b7fd6, type: 2}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b8873a2188a914424ba7539bcd65df5c, type: 3}
      price: 0
      isUnlocked: 0
  - characterName: Bob
    characterStory: "He has been the underdog all his life.  He has often experienced
      defeat but remains a believer that through hard work and perseverance he will
      eventually succeed.  He is always the sentimental favorite of the crowd.  He
      is the old warhorse \u2013 the veteran! Over time he has learned to be the
      best-prepared competitor mentally and physically.  He is in great physical
      shape and takes care of his body.  He eats the right things.  He is often found
      in the weight room.\n\nAlthough he has suffered numerous injuries (crashes)
      throughout his athletic career, he has learned to deal with them.  He understands
      that life isn\u2019t always fair.\n\nBob's messages \u2013 Be physically fit. 
      Take care of your equipment.  Deal with the disappointments.  \u201CDust off
      the snow, hold your head high and try again.\u201D \n\nBob\u2019s mark \u2013
      a chiseled body."
    characterModel: {fileID: 9058947439414178410}
    price: 1500
    isUnlocked: 0
    selectedSkinIndex: 0
    skins:
    - skinName: 
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 8748892135801146194, guid: f1a3d4d5cec5e441db0e3e1c65e26319, type: 3}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c07eb508fdf6f4c8dbd4aaaa19a99a7e, type: 3}
      price: 0
      isUnlocked: 0
    - skinName: 
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: 592cbdbea00064893b79664a9e05d82c, type: 2}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4bf1eb8203b0e4c8ba7dbfd1ed108508, type: 3}
      price: 0
      isUnlocked: 0
    - skinName: 
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: 068015a1b0cc440eda9a04e73367a601, type: 2}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b01af5452c76544179dfc37d379e6caa, type: 3}
      price: 0
      isUnlocked: 0
  - characterName: Sled
    characterStory: "Bob's cousin.  He is the comedian of the family.  Everyone likes
      him.  He is never serious except when he competes.  He doesn\u2019t like to
      practice.  He likes to play.  He encourages everyone to be the best they can
      be and most important \u2013 to have fun in life.  He loves his life and what
      he is doing.  He is living his dream.  He appears at all the competitions to
      cheer his family members on.  He is genuinely a good person.  He is always
      there to help out. \n\nSled's message \u2013 Be loyal.  Do what you love to
      do.  Have fun.\n\nSled's mark \u2013 a big smile."
    characterModel: {fileID: 908294412918592369}
    price: 1500
    isUnlocked: 0
    selectedSkinIndex: 0
    skins:
    - skinName: 
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: f0721e11c7b1d464c89fd0ae6ea2ec50, type: 2}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c28b2ae1e07c141d8a801d027855ef3e, type: 3}
      price: 0
      isUnlocked: 0
    - skinName: 
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: 7b56d3c34e79d46debb1eab8d7ebbfeb, type: 2}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: eae22073d30674560ba4ad63501c840e, type: 3}
      price: 0
      isUnlocked: 0
    - skinName: 
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: a1a53afbed07c44eb84c45cc42c68261, type: 2}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ee051418a04494780a7af1ce48130665, type: 3}
      price: 0
      isUnlocked: 0
  - characterName: Ski
    characterStory: "The captain of the Winter Sports team and the leader of the
      Family.  Tall and thin, Ski is always having fun. He enjoys life and is forever
      enthusiastic.  He is never down.  Ski\u2019s theme is to be positive.  He is
      the one that keeps the family up.  He encourages his teammates in good times
      and in bad times.\n\nSki is always moving and in a hurry to get places.  He
      has non-stop energy.  He loves speed.  He loves the beauty of the mountains
      and always takes the time to smell the fresh air and to \u201Csmell the roses.\u201D 
      He believes in himself and lives life every day with a total commitment to
      being the best.\n\nSki\u2019s message \u2013 Be positive and enthusiastic. 
      Enjoy the moment.  Think like a winner. Avoid the negative.\n\nSki\u2019s mark
      \u2013 Sunglasses and always coming to a screeching halt after speeding to
      the scene of the action."
    characterModel: {fileID: 8523012678108227409}
    price: 1500
    isUnlocked: 0
    selectedSkinIndex: 0
    skins:
    - skinName: 1
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 8748892135801146194, guid: 3bca75d0f19aa494aa660d05e402ad72, type: 3}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8fe8f7c86ac074473adb846e890dc4a7, type: 3}
      price: 100
      isUnlocked: 1
    - skinName: 2
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 0}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 599a46767d943461a94907668c58cd2a, type: 3}
      price: 200
      isUnlocked: 0
    - skinName: 
      skinMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: 0e5677f766c4c466eb571384ecfdea67, type: 2}
      skin: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a2554342c73bf4b5fbdf54ae8fb15e9c, type: 3}
      price: 0
      isUnlocked: 0
  - characterName: Puck
    characterStory: "Puck\u2019s theme is teamwork.  He knows the importance of teamwork
      because of his association with hockey.  His greatest thrill in life was when
      he won a gold medal during a past Olympiad. \n\nPuck is always on the move. 
      He moves swiftly and with direction.  His home is the goal, his bed is the
      net, and his playground is the ice.  He loves being curled up in the head of
      a hockey stick and he loves the rush he gets as he is pushed off the stick
      and headed to his home.\n\nPuck\u2019s messages \u2013 Play hard and Teamwork
      \u2013 \u201Cyou do better when you work together.\u201D\n\nPuck\u2019s mark
      \u2013 the gold medal he won at a past Olympiad displayed prominently on his
      body."
    characterModel: {fileID: 1244909148772978058}
    price: 2000
    isUnlocked: 0
