  - characterName: Board
    characterStory: "He lives on the edge.  Board\u2019s theme is \u201Cdare to be
      great.\u201D  He is always looking forward to his next big challenge.  He is
      like a rockstar to the younger generation.\n\nHe loves the outdoors and the
      snow under his body as he speeds and cuts down a mountain or does his thing
      while performing in the halfpipe competition.  He loves performing spins and
      somersaults in front of wildly cheering crowds.  He is always prepared to pay
      the price of success \u2013 hard work and a lot of practice.\n\nBoard\u2019s
      messages \u2013 Have No Fear.  Test Your Limits.  Go the Extra Mile.\n\nBoard\u2019s
      mark \u2013 A winked eye and an earring."
    characterModel: {fileID: 5921196442617673983}
    price: 500
    isUnlocked: 1
